  "instructions": [
    "Wash the fish fillet and pat it dry with paper towels.",
    "Slice the fish into thin, bite sized pieces.",
    "Place the fish in a shallow bowl and sprinkle with sea salt.",
    "Add the lime and lemon juice, making sure the fish is completely submerged.",
    "Stir in minced garlic, sliced chili, and freshly ground black pepper.",
    "Let the mixture marinate at room temperature for 5 minutes.",
    "While the fish marinates, chop the red onion, cucumber, cilantro, and avocado into small cubes.",
    "After 5 minutes, remove the fish from the bowl and drain any excess liquid.",
    "Combine the fish with the chopped vegetables and drizzle with optional fish sauce.",
    "Serve immediately with a side of crisp corn tortilla chips."
  ],
